## 2. File & Directory Management

Master file operations, navigation, and manipulation.

| Command | Description | Example Usage | Visual/Diagram Explanation |
|---------|-------------|---------------|----------------------------|
| `touch` | Create empty file or update timestamp | `touch newfile.txt`<br>`touch file{1..5}.txt` | `[Empty] â†’ touch â†’ [ğŸ“„ file created]` |
| `mkdir` | Make directory | `mkdir projects`<br>`mkdir -p dir1/dir2/dir3` | `ğŸ“ parent â†’ mkdir child â†’ ğŸ“ parent/child` |
| `rm` | Remove files or directories | `rm file.txt`<br>`rm -rf folder/` | `ğŸ“„ file â†’ rm â†’ [DELETED] âš ï¸ PERMANENT` |
