| `mv` | Move or rename files | `mv old.txt new.txt`<br>`mv file.txt /tmp/` | `ğŸ“„ A [location1] â†’ mv â†’ ğŸ“„ A [location2]` |
| `cat` | Concatenate and display files | `cat file.txt`<br>`cat file1 file2 > merged` | `ğŸ“„ â†’ cat â†’ [Display Content on Screen]` |
